<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT90">
<l>vīṟṟiruntu viṇṇāḷa vēṇṭuvār vēṅkaṭattāṉ</l>
<l>pāltirunta vaittārē paṉmalarkaṇ mēltirunta</l>
<l>vāḻvār varumatipārt taṉpiṉarāy maṟṟavarkkē</l>
<l>tāḻvā yiruppār tamar</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>People who wish to rule over heaven sitting [there] in distinction</l>
<l>are those who properly place many flowers by the side of [the Lord of] Vēṅkaṭam.</l>
<l>[But] will live perfectly [compared to] the above those who belong to the people,</l>
<l>who become devoted [to Him], watching the thoughts that occur [to Him],</l>
<l rend="indent">and prostrate themselves in worship before Him.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
